	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />MSCDEX is only half the battle, you also need a CD ROM driver in your config.sys.  Fortunately, the ATAPI standard made things much easier so you only need a common ATAPI driver instead of some driver that works with a particular sound card.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


